          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1701171841712-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and chop your <strong>carrot[s] </strong>into batons</p><p>Add your <strong>carrot batons</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 3-4 min or until the carrots are tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the carrots and return to the pot with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1701171853510-x200.jpg",
