    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 175ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[230ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1701171867761-x200.jpg",
